featured_reviews.review_id:
Masjid e Aqsa Yemkanmrdi me hi ek Masjid hai ma sha Allah bht acchi msjid hai zyada badi to nahi hai pr bht acchi hai.
Bahr ki traf masjid ka sahan hai. Kitchen hai sath hi me storeroom bhi hai wazu khana aur bathroom ka bhi intzaam hai.
Masjid ke ander ki traf 3 safo ki jaga hai aur bahr ki janib 2 safhe hai uske alawa ma sha Allah bada sahn bhi hai.
Is masjid me Jumma ki namaz hoti hai aur Qareeb ke dusre masajid se phle yaha hoti hai.
Masjid me dakhil hote waqt hame dua ka ahtmam krna chahiye..ALLAHUM_MAFTAHLI ABWABA RHMATIK.ya Allah mere liye Rahmat ke darwaze khol dijiye.
Isi trah Masjid se niklte waqt bhi dua pdhni chahiye.ALLAHUMMA INNI AS,ALUK MIN FAZLIK...ya Allah mai aapse aapke Fazl ka sawal krta hu.
Q k jitni bhi kaam hamare sunnat k mutabik hoge hamari zindagi utni hi barkat wali aur kamyab hogi.
JazakAllahu khair.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Masjid e Aqsa is a mosque in Yemkanmrdi but it is a very good mosque. It is not very big but it is very good.
The traffic outside is the source of the mosque. There is a kitchen, there is also a storeroom, there is provision for a bathroom and a bathroom.
The traffic inside the mosque is 3 clean and the outside is 2 clean. Apart from that, Allah is also very merciful.
Jumma prayers are held in this mosque and it is held here before the second mosque of Qareeb.
While entering the Masjid, we should pray... ALLAHUM_MAFTAHLI ABWABA RHMATIK. Ya Allah, open the doors of mercy for me.
Similarly, while leaving the Masjid, one should pray twice. ALLAHUMMA INNI AS, ALUK MIN FAZLIK... Ya Allah I have asked myself about your grace.
Because the more work we do in accordance with our Sunnah, the more our life will be blessed and achieved.
JazakAllahu khair.
